{"tid":1077683,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"小米展示100W快充技術,  4000mah電池17分充滿","createTime":"2019-03-25T18:13:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-14T03:10:21.000Z","uid":66271,"like":6,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"7123373d408a4a4b0474160c5b49eeafcbe4df58","tid":1077683,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T18:13:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?resize=2000%2C2000%2Cshrink&amp;image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2019-03%2F89a07bc0-4f1e-11e9-bfed-305f0ed5a335&amp;client=a1acac3e1b3290917d92&amp;signature=e4ef3689bf18759b5a9e41b38790c40b26a064b8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fo.aolcdn.com%2Fimages%2Fdims%3Fresize%3D2000%252C2000%252Cshrink%26image_uri%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fs.yimg.com%252Fos%252Fcreatr-uploaded-images%252F2019-03%252F89a07bc0-4f1e-11e9-bfed-305f0ed5a335%26client%3Da1acac3e1b3290917d92%26signature%3De4ef3689bf18759b5a9e41b38790c40b26a064b8&h=2315f771&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n小米現在似乎養成了靠工程機來秀肌肉的習慣，繼上次的雙折疊螢幕手機之後，公司總裁林斌剛剛又在微博上發佈了一段短片，內容是展示小米的 100W 快充。影片中同樣沒電的一台小米工程機和另一台 Oppo R17 Pro 被併排放在了一起，兩者同時開始充電。其中小米的那台內建了 4,000mAh 電池，在開機充了大概 17 分鐘後電量便被灌飽（功率的實際峰值大概在 88W 左右）。而關機用 50W SuperVOOC 充電的 R17 Pro，同一刻的電量「只」充到了 65%，很顯然小米又是在暗示自己能為別家廠商所不能了。<br />\n<br />\n這個 demo 乍看之下確實會讓人覺得非常厲害，不過問題是小米的這個技術並未真正量產，而 Oppo 那邊搭載 SuperVOOC 的手機都已經賣了大半年了。老實講這樣子的比較實際意義並不是很大，而且不光我們，Oppo 最近的網紅高管沈義人也是這麼覺得啦。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?resize=2000%2C2000%2Cshrink&amp;image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2019-03%2Fa6e85d10-4f1e-11e9-b00a-909fb7aa231f&amp;client=a1acac3e1b3290917d92&amp;signature=0fae0b7932289d089322c77175cbe06f6789bb92\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fo.aolcdn.com%2Fimages%2Fdims%3Fresize%3D2000%252C2000%252Cshrink%26image_uri%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fs.yimg.com%252Fos%252Fcreatr-uploaded-images%252F2019-03%252Fa6e85d10-4f1e-11e9-b00a-909fb7aa231f%26client%3Da1acac3e1b3290917d92%26signature%3D0fae0b7932289d089322c77175cbe06f6789bb92&h=dd795b0f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4e0eed22a50e3d317edecf06aaf032b6895e8c97","tid":1077683,"uid":30067,"like":74,"dislike":2,"score":72,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T18:30:32.000Z","msg":"下次整個1000W快充<br />\n要有電工B牌先俾差電"},{"pid":"ea14dab2cdbf24a1cb802821dc9974ea09376e7c","tid":1077683,"uid":117584,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T18:36:58.000Z","msg":"爆都爆得快d<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"420477f8bd9bc5aa167a3be8978d26471cadf024","tid":1077683,"uid":45368,"like":12,"dislike":12,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea14dab2cdbf24a1cb802821dc9974ea09376e7c","tid":1077683,"uid":117584,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T18:36:58.000Z","msg":"爆都爆得快d<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T18:47:56.000Z","msg":"好似都唔多聽到小米會爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ecfca46a66d65cc18333357145bb158e73fee87","tid":1077683,"uid":179051,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T18:50:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e4b7c03f34131497ac17620ba3d885906a25b479","tid":1077683,"uid":40226,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"420477f8bd9bc5aa167a3be8978d26471cadf024","tid":1077683,"uid":45368,"like":12,"dislike":12,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea14dab2cdbf24a1cb802821dc9974ea09376e7c","tid":1077683,"uid":117584,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T18:36:58.000Z","msg":"爆都爆得快d<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T18:47:56.000Z","msg":"好似都唔多聽到小米會爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T19:28:38.000Z","msg":"大陸好似有爆過<br />\n香港冇"},{"pid":"984beae3724fd2ffa9f7cc92a42765cad32a10b6","tid":1077683,"uid":27664,"like":0,"